The '''Great Hall''' was a magnificent and gargantuan room within [[Peacebringer's palace]] on [[Shiva IV]] used for assemblies and celebrations. It was here that a celebration occurred when the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] was defeated on Shiva IV.

